 “A party to a proceeding under subsection (d) or (e) of this section may bring a civil action in an appropriate district court of the United States for judicial review of the decision of the Secretary not later than 60 days after the decision becomes final.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (g). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/59/s7123/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–59, § 7123(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated subsec. (h) as (g). Former subsec. (g) redesignated (f)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsecs. (h), (i). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/59/s7123/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–59, § 7123(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated subsecs. (h) and (i) as (g) and (h), respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/59/s7122/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–59, § 7122(d)","children":[],"tail":", added subsecs. (h) and (i)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2002—Subsecs. (a), (b)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/296"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–296","children":[],"tail":" substituted “chapter, a regulation prescribed under this chapter, or a hazardous materials transportation security regulation or directive issued by the Secretary of Homeland Security” for “chapter or a regulation prescribed under this chapter” wherever appearing."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1994—Subsecs. (a), (b)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/429"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–429","children":[],"tail":" inserted “and unless authorized by another law of the United States” after “section” in introductory provisions."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b)(1)(E). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/311/s117/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–311, § 117(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “a packaging or a” for “a package or”."}],"tail":"\n